  "detailed_description": "<strong>Climb to the heavens across worlds, avoiding dangerous enemies in this \"Souls-Like\" game.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/3849f5026b84efc31d6d661f84a9b2dc.poster.avif?t=1766847020\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/3849f5026b84efc31d6d661f84a9b2dc.webm?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/3849f5026b84efc31d6d661f84a9b2dc.mp4?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/52f1e107368d3e863f319bfcee24bd41.avif?t=1766847020\" width=620 height=150 /></span><br><br>⭐⭐⭐<br>- Climb to the top using jumps and bounces off the wall.<br>- Dodge arrows and other projectiles of enemies who want to prevent your ascent!<br>- Open shortcuts to get back from a fall faster!<br>- Light a campfire to teleport to other precincts!<br>- Rest by the campfire to replenish the player's health and resources.<br>- Souls-Like combat system. Enemy Targer-Lock, Dodge, roll, block.<br>⭐⭐⭐<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6aa67d84baf2e25c4c9de5e508b23cfd.poster.avif?t=1766847020\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6aa67d84baf2e25c4c9de5e508b23cfd.webm?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6aa67d84baf2e25c4c9de5e508b23cfd.mp4?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/1b18f7fe8e5b290fed700cf432ff558a.avif?t=1766847020\" width=620 height=150 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6e3fab5e897020cee79f97b918022741.poster.avif?t=1766847020\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6e3fab5e897020cee79f97b918022741.webm?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6e3fab5e897020cee79f97b918022741.mp4?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>⭐⭐⭐<br>- You play as \"Kyoko\" a spirit who needs to climb to heaven to save his people. <br>- Get there as fast as possible , and compare your results with other players and friends.  <br>- A wide variety of worlds and obstacles await you, from winter to desert. <br>- Use your katana to make a series of strikes against your opponent.<br>- Explore the world to find auxiliary items.<br>- Bypass your opponents to deliver the fatal blow and ease the climb.<br>⭐⭐⭐",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Climb to the heavens across worlds, avoiding dangerous enemies in this \"Souls-Like\" game.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/3849f5026b84efc31d6d661f84a9b2dc.poster.avif?t=1766847020\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/3849f5026b84efc31d6d661f84a9b2dc.webm?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/3849f5026b84efc31d6d661f84a9b2dc.mp4?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/52f1e107368d3e863f319bfcee24bd41.avif?t=1766847020\" width=620 height=150 /></span><br><br>⭐⭐⭐<br>- Climb to the top using jumps and bounces off the wall.<br>- Dodge arrows and other projectiles of enemies who want to prevent your ascent!<br>- Open shortcuts to get back from a fall faster!<br>- Light a campfire to teleport to other precincts!<br>- Rest by the campfire to replenish the player's health and resources.<br>- Souls-Like combat system. Enemy Targer-Lock, Dodge, roll, block.<br>⭐⭐⭐<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6aa67d84baf2e25c4c9de5e508b23cfd.poster.avif?t=1766847020\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6aa67d84baf2e25c4c9de5e508b23cfd.webm?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6aa67d84baf2e25c4c9de5e508b23cfd.mp4?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/1b18f7fe8e5b290fed700cf432ff558a.avif?t=1766847020\" width=620 height=150 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6e3fab5e897020cee79f97b918022741.poster.avif?t=1766847020\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6e3fab5e897020cee79f97b918022741.webm?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2812910/extras/6e3fab5e897020cee79f97b918022741.mp4?t=1766847020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>⭐⭐⭐<br>- You play as \"Kyoko\" a spirit who needs to climb to heaven to save his people. <br>- Get there as fast as possible , and compare your results with other players and friends.  <br>- A wide variety of worlds and obstacles await you, from winter to desert. <br>- Use your katana to make a series of strikes against your opponent.<br>- Explore the world to find auxiliary items.<br>- Bypass your opponents to deliver the fatal blow and ease the climb.<br>⭐⭐⭐",
